room_title: Escape room "Inside Area 51" by Back in Time Escape Rooms in Los Angeles
room_address: 23700 S Western Ave Harbor City, CA 90710
room_description: You and your team must travel back to 1997 during the time of the evacuation immediately following the "accident" in the Roswell area and recover the individual's research notebook. This notebook contains evidence that can expose once and for all the true purpose of Area 51 to the public. Can you and your team break through the veil of secrecy and security to accomplish this mission?
